faqs.question: I have questions. How can I know more about a service?
faqs.answer: To know more about a service, read service related FAQs or Contact Us.

faqs.question: Can I upgrade from Standard to Premium?
faqs.answer: Yes, upgrades are possible. Contact us at intervieweecoach@thecoachr.com or WhatsApp for details.

faqs.question: There is an issue with the payment gateway. Whom to contact?
faqs.answer: Contact us at intervieweecoach@thecoachr.com or WhatsApp with details of the problem faced by you. We will resolve it and confirm as early as possible.
